 |________________ .---------------.
  ________________ | R e l e a s e | I n f o r m a t i o n . .
 |                 `----------------------------- -
 
 Void Eternal is a strategic God-game with rogue-like elements.
 You are a god watching over the people of Light and the people
 of Darkness, interlocked in an everlasting struggle for resources
 and survival.
 
 You have to carefully balance the expansionism of the people of
 Light, building up their economy and exploiting the resources of
 the land, with the aggressiveness of the people of Darkness,
 constantly attacking and collecting the Souls of their enemies.
 
 The world is flat, the people of Light living on the upper side,
 the people of Darkness living on the lower side. You have to
 expand the land into the Void surrounding it and explore exotic
 parallel dimensions with unique properties.
 
 While exploring the infinite, procedurally generated world, you
 will discover new resources, artifacts which can be researched
 to gain new technologies but also an old enemy who aims to wipe
 out both the people of Light and Darkness, leaving behind only
 eternal void.
